                         datasetid  = 'GHCND',

ncdc_ids = ncdc_ids$data

Plot Max Temperature

plot(x       = Date,
     y       = tmax, 
     type    = "p", 
     pch     = ".",   # as points
     col     = "red", 
     lwd     = 1.5, 
     cex.lab = 1.25,
     xlab    = "Date", 
     ylab    = "Max Temperature (deg C)",
     main    = station_name_label)

Convert to a CSV File.



  targ_time_series_raw                      = data.frame(date = Date)
  

  
  targ_time_series_raw$max_temperature = targ_data$tmax
  targ_time_series_raw$min_temperature = targ_data$tmin
  targ_time_series_raw$precipitation   = targ_data$pcpn
  targ_time_series_raw$snowfall        = targ_data$snow
  targ_time_series_raw$snowdepth       = targ_data$snwd

  
    
  output_file_name = paste(file_title_string,
                           ".csv",
                           sep="")
  
  write.table(x    = targ_time_series_raw, 
              file = output_file_name, 
              sep  =", ",
              row.names = FALSE)
